---client server model---

 --- Node JS , server ke side hota h , gaanth bandh lo ---

-> client gives request and server gives responses
-> Now there are two types of languages 
    client site language : HTML , CSS , Javascript
    server site language : NODE JS , python , java , php (the languages which can be connected with databases are called as server site languages)
-> node js internally uses Javascript using V8 engine
-> V8 engine is written in C++
-> Node Js is moslty create APIs , so we can connect client and server .
-> Website can be made using Node JS , but its rare.
